        <amcr:popis>Location Libeň (at the foot of the slope; 430,5 m above sea level). The foothills of the long spine of Libeň, between Novodvorsky and Doomsday Creek; Z from the location of Ranch at Doomsday Creek. Regular, rectangular enclosures formed of berms and trenches measuring 80 x 200 metres, with raised corners. A large columned structure, two semi-earthworks and other objects were uncovered in the grounds.</amcr:popis>
